<X3D profile="Immersive" version="4.0">
<head>
  <meta name="title" content="Northwest Breccia Fan (floor sub-space) (Potter Creek)"/>
  <meta name="description" content="The fan landform sloping from the NW end and coalescing at mid-chamber, its apex under the NW chimney, the full A-H sequence with stratum As 13.5 ft greatest clay depth; that C (ash) and the G chocolate-mud are barren."/>
  <meta name="rights" content="Interpretive: Footprint (~50 x 30 ft read off the plan), apex height, and that the cumulative A-H stack is a render composite of greatest thicknesses, NOT additive measured depth. LAYOUT: global_position/level_orde"/>
</head>
